It seems that exported is `__pyx_memoryview_check` which should be `inline` function:

https://github.com/cython/cython/blob/016459711f5d845933b1f46f273e695f43810dc4/Cython/Utility/MemoryView.pyx#L665-L666

And truly, the resulting binary does contain   `__pyx_memoryview_check` symbol:

```
$ nm _cyutility.cpython-314-x86_64-linux-gnu.so | grep memoryview_check
000000000000b180 t __pyx_memoryview_check
```

But regularly created .so file does not contain it:

```
$ nm bm_matrix.cpython-314-x86_64-linux-gnu.so | grep memoryview_check
$
```
